{"tid":985614,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"街坊隨意拍不經修圖　最高顏值男明星一定係吳亦凡？","createTime":"2019-01-17T17:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T06:43:07.000Z","uid":193951,"like":20,"dislike":409,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"e30a45354d46ced7142107086b85b753edb1eb74","tid":985614,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"當紅每個明星基本上都有數十個、甚至數百個屬於自己的個站，管理站子的管理員，常被稱為站姐。站姐們會在追行程時利用大砲（單反相機）拍攝高清照片，並在經過精心修圖後才會上載於個站，所以通常出來的偶像照片一定是完美無暇。然而，最真實的照片往往出自路人之手，路人往往只是偶爾遇上明星，又隨手用手機拍下了影片或照片，然後就直接上載社交媒體炫耀一番。這些自然的圖片或影片（又名：生圖）才能體現出明星真正的一面。以下為您盤點完美通過生圖考驗的男明星。<br />\n<br />\n黃旼泫（NU&rsquo;EST/WannaOne）<br />\n<br />\n暱稱：美年（韓文近音），見暱稱如見人，黃旼泫俊秀的外表、完美身型比例、甜美的嗓音、優秀的男朋友式穿搭技巧都使一眾粉絲被迷得神魂顛倒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNfZ0DY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNfZ0DY.jpg&h=1ef3f7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾（GOT7）<br />\n<br />\n香港界的代表，作為一個Rapper，除了有魅力的低音煙嗓，外貌也一點不輸蝕，還加上親民，怪不得人見人愛，成為圈中人脈王。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A76VyZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA76VyZH.jpg&h=8f457149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhkWirn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhkWirn.jpg&h=7d0baa77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL8HYro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL8HYro.jpg&h=b9b31b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBcqbMo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBcqbMo.jpg&h=26d3f3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seOs9x3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseOs9x3.jpg&h=2184cbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qh90K6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQh90K6p.jpg&h=8d810416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CgB2S4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CgB2S4.jpg&h=8e3c34fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n崔珉豪（SHINee）<br />\n<br />\n出身於顏值聞名的SM家，更是偶像團體中門面的表表者，朝著演員方向走也是理所當然吧！無公害的小鹿相，加上親和的性格，優越的身型比例，還不是人群中最閃耀的星！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQ7tT0m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQ7tT0m.jpg&h=8a745dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炎亞綸<br />\n<br />\n作為台灣初代偶像團體飛輪海的成員，很多90後的偶像，雖然今年已經出道十四年，但顏值依然十年如一日，完全可以融入一班小鮮肉之中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1R5OT0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1R5OT0Q.jpg&h=c4c92aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳亦凡<br />\n<br />\n模特兒的身高、帥氣的臉蛋、帶點痞痞的氣質，就像是從漫畫裡走出來的人物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXkWisU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXkWisU.jpg&h=b02ea7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckv3HUB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fckv3HUB.jpg&h=e8d7f423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDrFK7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDrFK7W.jpg&h=eaa9f218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2j0K7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2j0K7X.jpg&h=795ced1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NALbNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NALbNY.jpg&h=dab31883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpXJHUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpXJHUE.jpg&h=95d8197d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/283808/%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E9%9A%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%8D%E7%B6%93%E4%BF%AE%E5%9C%96-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F283808